snippet.title: The Under Games Expansion - Release Trailer - War for the Overworld
snippet.description:
The Under Games is here at last! Choose your Underlord and delve into our latest expansion. Available on Steam and GOG Now.

Buy it now on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/594630/
GOG: https://www.gog.com/game/war_for_the_overworld_the_under_games
Brightrock Store: https://store.brightrockgames.com/collections/our-games/products/wfto-the-under-games-expansion-digital-steam-key

Read the full release post here: https://wftogame.com/undergames-release/

Main website: http://www.wftogame.com
Forums: http://forum.brightrockgames.com
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/wftogame
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/wftogame
Discord: http://discord.gg/BrightrockGames
